    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A steampunk welding torch resembling a lightsaber hilt, its tip emitting a short jet of blue-white plasma flame. Used to repair and heal Delta Kilo Autarchs by welding damaged plating back into place. When used on a non-Autarch creature, the plasma flame instead burns and damages them.</p><h2>Construct Mending</h2><p>Target a Delta Kilo Autarch. Choose an intensity level (1-3 charges). No attack roll required.</p><h2>Plasma Burn</h2><p>Target a non-Autarch creature. Requires a successful attack roll against AC. Choose an intensity level (1-3 charges).</p><table><tr><th>Level</th><th>Charges</th><th>Formula</th></tr><tr><td>1</td><td>1</td><td>2d8 + spellcasting modifier + proficiency bonus</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>2</td><td>3d8 + spellcasting modifier + proficiency bonus</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>3</td><td>4d8 + spellcasting modifier + proficiency bonus</td></tr></table><p>If the wielder has no spellcasting ability, the spellcasting modifier is treated as +0. Charges are recovered on a short rest at a rate of the wielder's character level divided by 3 (rounded down), and fully restored on a long rest.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
